      &lt;img alt="A black Twitter logo over a red illustration" src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/yiRlXp9C2_eFT8dbjNG3wDD2KUM=/0x0:3000x2000/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73451878/acastro_STK050_08.0.jpg" /&gt;
